cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.CL 

This paper is about video understanding using a convolutional network architecture. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the efficiency of the network, which suggests that it could be relevant to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Multimedia (cs.MM) categories. Additionally, the paper involves reasoning and classification, which could place it in the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) category. Finally, the paper also mentions video captioning, which is a task related to Natural Language Processing (cs.CL).
